@startuml ActivityDiagram
' PlantUML activity diagram for data collection + weather integration + ML decision
skinparam monochrome true

title Activity: Data collection → ML decision → Alert/Logging

|Go Backend|
start
:Trigger data collection;

partition "Data Sources" {
  fork
    :Read sensor metrics;
  fork again
    :Request weather forecast (external API);
  end fork
}

:Merge sensor and weather features;
:Preprocess data (filter noise, normalize, enrich);

partition "ML Service" {
  :Send features to ML model (MLP);
  :Receive probability P;
}

if (P > 0.7) then (high risk)
  :Create urgent alert;
  :Notify stakeholders (email/WEBHOOK/SMS);
  -> Log alert to DB;
else (monitor)
  :Store monitoring entry in DB;
endif

stop
@enduml
